posting_body: ['Welcome Home to Gardens of Fontainbleu', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x136', 'From $3,264', '.', '1 Bed 1 Bath .', '720 Sq.Ft', '* Unit 206 - Available 08/20/22', '* Unit 327 - Available 09/24/22', '* Unit 328 - Available 09/24/22', 'Gardens of Fontainbleu', 'Address:', '10200 MILLER AVE Cupertino, CA 95014', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Come take a tour of your next luxurious one-bedroom, one-bathroom home at Gardens of Fontainbleu today.', 'The spacious kitchen reveals slab granite countertops that pairs well with the white cabinetry.', 'The Living room has ample space to entertain family and friends (who’s up for charades!?).', 'You will appreciate the added convenience of dual mirrored closets in the master suite and a private balcony for you to enjoy.', 'Living in this pet-friendly neighborhood also grants you access to a variety of incredible amenities.', 'Go for a swim in the lap pool, socialize with neighbors in the neighborhood clubhouse, or work out in the fitness center with strength and cardio equipment.', 'Neighbors can also take advantage of the many nearby restaurants, shops, and parks.', 'Contact a member of the leasing staff now for more information.', 'FLOORPLAN SPECIALS', '1 Month Free on Select Apartments', 'FLOORPLAN/UNIT\u2002 \u2002FEATURES', 'Additional Storage', 'Remodeled Kitchen', 'Patio', 'Large Patio', 'Appliances - Dishwasher', 'Fans - Ceiling', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Monday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x136', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
